latestPosts.caption:
After all the excitement of the pre-wedding celebrations, the big day finally arrived! We kicked things off bright and early with Sonal’s emotional bridal reveal on the balcony with her family — a truly unforgettable moment and one of the highlights of the day.
The jaan arrived in style, with dhol beats and dancing as everyone made their way to the mandap set on the hotel grounds near the beach. 

Sonal made a stunning entrance, lovingly escorted by her sister, and the ceremony, beautifully led by Ravi Shastri, was filled with warmth and joy.
We wrapped things up with some fun portraits by the beach — the perfect ending to a beautiful wedding.
